high_descs: Turn right, and go to the couch.
Pick up the tea pot on the floor, to the right of the couch.
Turn around, go toward the TV, then turn right, then go to the desk.
Place the tea pot on the desk, to the left of the box.
anns.task_desc: Put a tea pot on the desk.

high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the couch.
Pick up the watering plant that is on the ground to the right of the couch.
Turn around and walk towards the television, then hang a right and walk over to the black desk.
Place the watering can on the black desk to the right of the blue credit card.
anns.task_desc: Place a watering can on a black desk.

high_descs: Turn to the right  facing the sofa in front of you.
Pick up the watering can beside the plant in the corner.
Turn around to your left, then make a right until you are standing in front of the black desk.
Put the watering can on the desk near the box.
anns.task_desc: Putting the watering can on the black desk.
